desc_short	-----								Experience a true classic! This Gold edition includes the original Jagged Alliance plus the add-on Jagged Alliance: Deadly Games. Take a trip into retro land and learn why this is considered to be one the best turn-based games of all times. Choose your mercenaries wisely and lead them into battle against the evil Santino.							
